# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# SkillSync — Production Environment Variables (EXAMPLE)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Copy this file to .env.production.template and fill in real values.
# Set values in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables.
# NEVER commit real secrets to git — .env.production.template is gitignored.
#
# Legend:
#   [REQUIRED]  — App will crash at startup without this
#   [OPTIONAL]  — Has a sensible default or is a bonus feature
#   [PUBLIC]    — Safe to expose to browser (NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] PostgreSQL connection string
# For Vercel + Supabase: use the "Transaction" pooler URL (port 6543) for serverless.
# Format: postgresql://user:password@host:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: For serverless, use the connection POOLER URL, not the direct URL.
# Supabase Dashboard → Settings → Database → Connection string → "Transaction" mode
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.YOUR_SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF:YOUR_SUPABASE_DB_PASSWORD@aws-0-YOUR_REGION.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true

# ── NextAuth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] Your production domain (no trailing slash)
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://YOUR_APP_NAME.vercel.app

# [REQUIRED] Random secret for JWT signing. Generate with:
#   openssl rand -base64 32
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=YOUR_NEXTAUTH_SECRET_HERE

# ── Microsoft Azure AD OAuth ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] Azure Portal → App Registrations → your app
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_AZURE_CLIENT_ID_HERE
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=YOUR_AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET_HERE
MICROSOFT_TENANT_ID=YOUR_AZURE_TENANT_ID_HERE

# ⚠️  Update Redirect URIs in Azure Portal to include:
#   https://YOUR_APP_NAME.vercel.app/api/auth/callback/azure-ad

# ── Supabase ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY_HERE

# [REQUIRED] Server-only — never exposed to browser
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=YOUR_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY_HERE

# ── Cloudinary (Resume Storage) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] Cloudinary Dashboard → Account Details
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=YOUR_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME_HERE
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=YOUR_CLOUDINARY_API_KEY_HERE
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=YOUR_CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET_HERE

# ── AI Provider API Keys ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [OPTIONAL] At least ONE key is needed for AI features to work.
# The AntigravityRouter will use whichever providers have keys set.
GROQ_API_KEY=YOUR_GROQ_API_KEY_HERE
MISTRAL_API_KEY=YOUR_MISTRAL_API_KEY_HERE
GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY_HERE

# ── Redis (Optional) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [OPTIONAL] For background queues (if used)
REDIS_URL=redis://YOUR_REDIS_HOST:6379

# ── Role Assignment ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [OPTIONAL] Email domain for automatic student account creation
# Default: "stu.upes.ac.in"
STUDENT_EMAIL_DOMAIN=YOUR_STUDENT_EMAIL_DOMAIN_HERE

# ── Cron Jobs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [REQUIRED] Secret to authenticate Vercel Cron requests
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 48
CRON_SECRET=YOUR_CRON_SECRET_HERE

# ── Logging ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# [OPTIONAL] Log level: debug | info | warn | error
# Default: "info" (set to "warn" in production to reduce noise)
LOG_LEVEL=warn

# ── Telemetry ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1
